{"tid":905713,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"三日兩夜 千雪 靚湯","createTime":"2018-11-17T11:04:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T14:45:36.000Z","uid":38456,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"698ffa4c3271c4a73471058eaa0d341d1c253b11","tid":905713,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T11:04:02.000Z","msg":"朱千雪和湯洛雯自駕遊日本北海道，上網預約、帶齊證件，租車冇難度。醫肚先到札幌市的場外市場，海產應有盡有，即點即煮鮮味爆燈，千雪有多愛「大吞拿魚腩」？聽她細說。滑雪場夏天都有別開生面的活動，千雪和洛雯爬上樹頂歷險，是時候考驗彼此的友情！狸小路二百間店舖夠逛足一日，影貼紙相有幾cutie？睇片就知。到旭川市入住CP值高酒店，享受獨有導遊服務；品嚐甘酒、酒糟軟雪糕、流水麵、海膽涮涮鍋，隨時變增肥之旅。"},{"pid":"4427499158b70eb05e6ddd0f84a6bcbe69e088c7","tid":905713,"uid":184762,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T11:05:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c899732a621765f6bec8ca78275a533ad7d1343","tid":905713,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T11:09:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3c73fb62272ac20ce64e031fc36b8e6342bd05eb","tid":905713,"uid":55533,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T11:22:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"142dcb871ea6d88899725861a3fc84363701e5f2","tid":905713,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4c899732a621765f6bec8ca78275a533ad7d1343","tid":905713,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T11:09:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T12:01:22.000Z","msg":"1030"},{"pid":"3d63ba7df09628af73297da09ebe11fb972db850","tid":905713,"uid":123920,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T12:14:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\